      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="0da7729863212fdc" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: Fusion hounds move very fast and use that speed to their advantage in combat. A hound can move a long distance and still attack as a single action. It can also use its action to run about in random patterns, hindering attacks against it by two steps.</source>
        <target></target>
