      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="b884f23e8af86fd0" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Interaction: Fusion hounds are animals. Creatures immune to radiation sometimes train the hounds to become guardians or hunting dogs, but such creatures are rare.</source>
