      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="58708c2e7fe2e3b6" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Use: An NPC delivering something the characters need never made it to the rendezvous. If they backtrack to where the NPC should have come from, the PCs are attacked by a pack of fusion hounds on the road. Clearly, the courier was attacked by the pack as well, and the characters must discover if the NPC is dead or merely injured, and where the package now lies.</source>
        <target></target>
        <context-group name="" purpose="location">
